'''Alvord Independent School District''' is a public [[school district]] based in [[Alvord, Texas|Alvord]], [[Texas]] ([[United States|USA]]).

[[Image:alvordisd.gif|Center|Logo of Alvord Independent School District]]

The district is located in north central [[Wise County, Texas|Wise County]] and extends into a small portion of southern [[Montague County, Texas|Montague County]].

There are three schools in Alvord ISD - Alvord High (Grades 9-12), Alvord Middle (Grades 6-8), and Alvord Elementary (Grades PK-5)

